new york city shooting

List of every shooting incident that occurred in NYC going back to 2006 through the end of the previous calendar year.

Did the NYPD prevent the city from sliding back into the violence of previous eras. Here’s a look at recent shooting incidents and victims. The data is supplied by the NYPD.

NYPD_shooting <- read.csv("NYPD_Shooting_Incident_Data__Historic_.csv")
